    <title>Combined summary - Fees and the block-finding process</title>
    <updated>2025-10-11T22:07:54.275761+00:00</updated>
    <link href="https://gnusha.org/url/https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2015-August/009986.html" rel="alternate"/>
